::Hot Rod::

He didn't move at all. His eyes locked on Unicron. but unicron didn't
even bother to acknowlage him. Hot Rod was only a foot smaller.
He shot two missiles at Unicron.

::DrillBit/Dollon::

They both continued to fire on Unitron, but with no response.
"Whats with this guy?" Asked Dollon.
"Cybertron steroyeds?" Added DrillBit.

::Epyon::

He pulled to the side of the battle, and opened a link to base.
"I'm here. What is it Alpha?"

::Demolition::

This Wolfgang hadn't tryed anything, so he sat down, relaxing a bit.

::KitKat2::

She kept moving around the Alliance base.
'How the hell do I get out of here!' She thought.
She wamted to get back to the Pack.
